Propose a typed illustration for the following paragraph.

The output MUST be a JSON object with three fields:
- `aspect_ratio`: one of the eight ComfyUI `ResolutionSelector` aspect-ratio tokens — pick the one that best matches the visual composition of the scene. Valid values: "square", "photo", "portrait photo", "portrait standard", "standard", "widescreen portrait", "widescreen", "ultrawide".
- `megapixels`: target resolution in megapixels — typically 1.0 to 2.5. Higher values for hero shots; lower for transitional filler scenes. Must be a positive number.
- `prompt`: the image-generation prompt itself, written in ComfyUI tag format.

